    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Remove 2 <strong>outer lettuce leaves </strong>per person and set these aside for serving</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lettuce[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Slice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p>",
