      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
