      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>brioche rolls</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 4-5 min or until warmed through</p>",
