      "instruction": "<p>Fill your <strong>warmed brioche buns </strong>with the <strong>lettuce leaves</strong>, <strong>sliced tomato</strong>, <strong>fried chicken </strong>and <strong>sriracha mayo</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chips </strong>and <strong>lettuce halves </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the lettuce with the <strong>dressing </strong>and serve any <strong>remaining sriracha mayo </strong>to the side for dipping</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
